Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:26.41,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:31.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to the sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:37.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:45.01,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.81,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:47.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has faded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:53.31,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:53.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:58.53,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:58.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:04.12,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:04.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:09.66,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:09.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.92,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:11.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:15.25,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:15.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:20.51,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:20.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:26.05,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:26.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.52,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.41,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:47.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:55.43,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:55.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.79,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.13,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:01.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:06.30,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:06.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:12.02,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:12.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:17.48,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:17.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:25.50,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is rushing to Navy HQ to rescue his brother, Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is waiting to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The execution is in 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All forces of the Navy are expecting an attack by the Whitebeard Pirates at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, tell them the name of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother's name is Portgaz D. Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year and 3 months after the father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the child was born with the blood of the world's most heinous man in his veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King of the Pirates -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bloodline of the King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Vast Fleet Appears! Here Come the Whitebeard Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:05:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that the arch villain had a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of Gold Roger continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved that they got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's a son of the King of the Pirates, he must be atrocious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd caught him and put him up for auction, I would have made a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This execution is turning into quite a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the strength of "Fire Fist" is in his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he has the One Piece, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist" is as good as dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be wiped off the face of the earth soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:58.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(920,100)}"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not the biological brother of Luffy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His biological son alive! This must be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All people connected to Roger should have been executed at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since his brother is Luffy-san, I thought that his father was Dragon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so, too! What's the deal here? They're not biological brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe this, Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm expecting a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I won't be around by the time of the child's birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you telling that to me a Navy officer, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mother of the child--a woman related to you will be executed for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government will definitely dig up my whereabouts for the last year
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and find and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they can't blame a child whose not born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've tried to kill each other dozens of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can trust you as I trust my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must protect my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure that you'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure that it's this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People saw Roger acting like he wasn't a pirate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he were a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger's era has ended. We have to cut the bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find all the babies who are due within 10 months of his going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All pregnant women, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill all mothers who are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 were born in this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones who are due next month are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look into the ones with husbands, too. They could be fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:12:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll come back when she is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're no more pregnant women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 10 months since Roger went to jail. I think he has not child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Roger's time is really over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Portgaz D. Rouge, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a girl--Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a boy--Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the names that he picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his name is Gol D. Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rouge!\N--Rouge! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must raise him, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose baby is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You're gonna live with them from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta live with them! Be nice to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Luffy and I unfortunately have the blood of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the world's most infamous criminals in our veins anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took over the name "Portgaz" from my mother to whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never wanted to have my good-for-nothing father's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took over your mother's name and rose up in the world of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as the captain of the Spade Pirates with your exquisite speed and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when we noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Roger's blood still flowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Whitebeard also noticed that at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make you the next King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he let the son of his old rival onto his ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got on the ship to make my dad the next King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one believes that except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it made it harder for us to catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were protected by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let you go free, we know you'll use \Nyour abilities to become the next King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it means a great deal to execute you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means risking an all-out war with Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku! I have report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of Justice is opening without any order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't make contact with the control room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It'd be nice if it opened with a hit!\N--Oh, like "knock knock"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's all it'd take?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of Justice opens on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy guy told us that they weren't gonna open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The control room must be in Marineford. Who is doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go! A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out of joy, my blade bones are dancing the lambada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There! There we go, there we go, there we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ca-Captain Buggy, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you're opening it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a messenger of God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Buggy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not! What kind of role play is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously. Who is opening it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:19:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe God really wants me to become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's almost unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:20:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared so suddenly! Where did they get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the vast fleet of pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Whitebeard? Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bohemian Knight Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thunder Lord" McGuy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DeCalvan Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whirl Spider Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all big-time captains who are well known in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,43 ships in total! We can't find Whitebeard or the commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're all allies of Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-chan, can you see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for you, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! So pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect them to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shall we attack?\N--Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard should be somewhere near, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he must be up to something so keep an eye on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited! Just come on, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'll appear from where we least expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we got the wrong lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I see a shadow in the bay!\N--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now! They got all their ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...coated and approached from underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Moby Dick emerges right in the middle of Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On its deck, Whitebeard and his 14 commanders are ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates head straight for Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an unbroken bond between them an Ace, a family bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Beginning of the War! Ace and Whitebeard's Past!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
